title: Envy on the Coast - Lucy Gray (2007)
description:
Envy on the Coast&#039;s latest LP
Enjoy!

----
"Three years ago, two discouraged friends sat down and imagined what it would be like to play in band without gimmicks, without egos, and without facades. They wondered what it&#039;d be like to play with people who shared in their desire to meet every kid, at every show, in every state they played. Without even making a conscious attempt to pursue this concept, they were fortunate enough to find three other friends who shared this desire. Over the course of 3 years, Envy on the Coast was born."
